copy a directory to another directory

cd /home/md6270

find . -depth -print |cpio -pamVd /tmp/test

Next, if want to cpio up a directory do this

cd /appl/dpa

find . |cpio -odvum > /usr/openv/dpa_out.cpio

Now you want to extract the file

cd into directory, copy the file there

cpio -idvum < dpa_out.cpio
